The following Franklin County cases were decided in state supreme court.
                    Helser vs McGrath, judgement affirmed; Ritter vs Downey, judgement affirmed;
                    Wickey vs Eyster, judgement affirmed; Hetrick vs Smith, judgement affirmed;
                    Hughes vs Oaks, judgement affirmed; Cumberland Valley Railroad Company vs
                    M'Lanahan, judgement reversed; Schlosser vs Sollenberger, judgement reversed;
                    Knepper vs Kurtz, judgement affirmed.
